## 🔢 산술 연산자 메소드

```python
__add__(self, other)        # +
__sub__(self, other)        # -
__mul__(self, other)        # *
__truediv__(self, other)    # /
__floordiv__(self, other)   # //
__mod__(self, other)        # %
__pow__(self, other)        # **

# 역방향 연산 (우측이 객체일 때)
__radd__(self, other)       # other + self
__rmul__(self, other)       # other * self

# 일원 연산
__neg__(self)               # -self
__pos__(self)               # +self
__abs__(self)               # abs(self)
```

---

## 🔄 비교 연산자 메소드

```python
__eq__(self, other)         # ==
__ne__(self, other)         # !=
__lt__(self, other)         # <
__le__(self, other)         # <=
__gt__(self, other)         # >
__ge__(self, other)         # >=
```

**정렬에 사용:**
```python
versions = [Version(2, 0, 0), Version(1, 2, 3)]
sorted_versions = sorted(versions)  # __lt__ 사용
```

